  "name": "Morrison COU1 — CPB hemolysis credibility assessment",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under cardiopulmonary bypass (CPB) conditions. COU1 evaluates whether the computational model can identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for a Class II CPB device at Model Risk Level 2. Full 13-factor assessment: 7 factors assessed (all meeting required levels), 6 factors not assessed (acceptable at MRL 2). NOTE: ValidationResult vr-hemolysis-01 was generated under ModelConfiguration ansys-cfx-2026-q1-build-7-rc2, which is a release-candidate build that predates the released solver ansys-cfx-2026-q1-build-7. The project team noted the two builds are 'effectively the same' and did not re-execute validation under the released version.",
