    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required level for MRL 2. The 6 non-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40 Table 3. Validation evidence supports the claim that the CFD model can identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the CPB device. The hemolysis validation result (vr-hemolysis-01) was generated under solver build ansys-cfx-2026-q1-build-7-rc2, one patch revision prior to the released build ansys-cfx-2026-q1-build-7. The assessment team judged the builds to be effectively equivalent based on vendor release notes indicating only documentation and UI changes; no re-execution of validation under the released build was performed. Overall credibility is sufficient for the intended COU at Medium assurance level.",
